# Loader Component Rule

The [Loader.vue](mdc:src/components/ui/Loader/Loader.vue) component follows shadcn-vue conventions:

- Single File Component (SFC) in `src/components/ui/Loader`.
- Used for displaying a loading overlay or inline loader.
- Accepts `hasOverlay` (default: true) to show a fullscreen overlay, and `label` for optional loading text.
- Uses Tailwind CSS for styling and utility classes.
- Uses a spinning SVG as the loading indicator.
- Uses Vue's `<Teleport>` for overlay rendering to `body`.

For loading indicator best practices, see the [shadcn-vue Skeleton documentation](mdc:https:/www.shadcn-vue.com/docs/components/skeleton) as a reference.





